snippet.textDisplay: Krewella and Riaz Qadri collaboration!!! Runaway and "Mudatan Beet Gaiyan"!!!!! No piece of music can be expected to be more unique and interesting than this one. How do you mix the two polar opposite genres of music into a harmonious song.  That's going to be a masterpiece!!!! Thank you to Ali Hamza for thinking outside the box and reaching out to Krewella and honoring their art and their heritage. Jahan and Yasmine are so proud of their half Pakistani heritage and I hope the Desi Krew will sense this pride via this song and connect with them on a deeper level.
snippet.textOriginal: Krewella and Riaz Qadri collaboration!!! Runaway and "Mudatan Beet Gaiyan"!!!!! No piece of music can be expected to be more unique and interesting than this one.
